# ⚓ Global Bridge

This file connects this project's local intelligence to the **Global Foundation**.

## Pointer
- **Global Root**: `C:/Users/USER/AndroidStudioProjects/_foundation/.agents` (Replace with your absolute path to the global .agents folder)

## Resolution Protocol
1.  Load shared **Rules** from `<Global Root>/rules/common/`.
2.  Inherit **Skills** from `<Global Root>/skills/`.
3.  Execute **Workflows** from `<Global Root>/workflows/`.

> [!NOTE]
> If a file exists both locally and in the Global Root, the **Local** version always takes precedence.
